{"tid":383520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"]大圍港鐵站外執勤　食環署職員報稱遇襲倒地","createTime":"2017-09-01T14:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T02:55:38.000Z","uid":53379,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da8d890eb699410b4efac325adf7847ba1446107","tid":383520,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:12:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大圍港鐵站外執勤　食環署職員報稱遇襲倒地</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/taiwai_FuDWZ_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ftaiwai_FuDWZ_1200x0.png&h=0de7b7a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n9月1日大圍站外有食環署職員躺在地上（Facebook片段截圖）<br />\n今日傍晚6時許，多名食環署職員在大圍港鐵站外執勤時報稱遇襲。一男一女的食環署職員，以及另一名男子均倒在地上。不過有圍觀市民就質疑，眾人是否假扮受傷。<br />\n<br />\n由網上流傳的影片可見，兩名食環署人員躺在地上動彈不得。另一食環署職員呼籲圍觀的民眾散開，向傷者給予空間。不少民眾即質疑，倒地食環署人員是否真的有受傷：「傷者？」、「老虎都打死幾隻啦！」、「受傷仲棟得起隻腳？」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》指，食環署職員在大圍港鐵站外執勤時報稱遇襲，警方接報到場後，暫列襲擊傷人案，並在現場展開調查。《香港01》報道稱，事件中有市民亂拋垃圾，食環署人員上前檢控時被襲倒地。報道引消息指事件中其實有4人受傷，包括2男1女食環署人員及一名男子，他們被送往威爾斯親王醫院接受治理。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》正向警方查詢案情，暫未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/大圍港鐵站外執勤-食環署職員報稱遇襲倒地/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8D%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%AB%99%E5%A4%96%E5%9F%B7%E5%8B%A4-%E9%A3%9F%E7%92%B0%E7%BD%B2%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E5%A0%B1%E7%A8%B1%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2%E5%80%92%E5%9C%B0%2F&d=jNqal1Y62jF460GvPJUSj26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=a4aa6658\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8D%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%AB%99%E5%A4%96%E5%9F%B7%E5%8B%A4-%E9%A3%9F%E7%92%B0%E7%BD%B2%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E5%A0%B1%E7%A8%B1%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2%E5%80%92%E5%9C%B0%2F&h=81b6d5b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/大圍港鐵站外執勤-食環署職員報稱遇襲倒地/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1665175766848584&amp;id=100000685312021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1665175766848584%26id%3D100000685312021&d=jNqal1Y62jF460GvPJUSj26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=819f141d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1665175766848584&amp;id=100000685312021</a>"},{"pid":"35ccf1267d4d2c674da303d5aaab6b2cfd2503e9","tid":383520,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:13:42.000Z","msg":"柒"},{"pid":"ac6af704c35af52bc9e7c046e182f568feab00a5","tid":383520,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:15:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ebaece860568fa18767f43479e3b0eec72c1bd","tid":383520,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:19:17.000Z","msg":"人渣"},{"pid":"41b7d422b61538ffb6d491817e7dc26dd6a9167e","tid":383520,"uid":73722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:23:57.000Z","msg":"出賣良知，賺廿幾K一個月，大量津貼兼長俸，訓街3分鐘可以呃半個月病假，你做唔做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我做埋你個份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c276ffd1551b22a29af3faeaf891f930ac8dd9","tid":383520,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:26:25.000Z","msg":"訓地下算唔算阻街？"},{"pid":"b74f77de1ccc745501059f967a52e29fb12de1d6","tid":383520,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:27:00.000Z","msg":"其實條肥仔係咪中毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9d2bcbd59d915f55578db2c28d64185c9b8eeb","tid":383520,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:28:50.000Z","msg":"插水"},{"pid":"e803d7face2239931e0b7dbb3c6f6e22fc7d19e4","tid":383520,"uid":2819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:34:00.000Z","msg":"櫻桃直飛"},{"pid":"4229d0d2a2c38c5a26bc024abd1a8613121cbe13","tid":383520,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:51:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f042fa15bafc48cdc48a1ddcac7f8cd97c8cb13c","tid":383520,"uid":16864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:52:28.000Z","msg":"真係好撚肉酸<br />\n扮死"},{"pid":"2d944f00a9836461348aded4422d05e40f4327e9","tid":383520,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T01:57:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">男子亂拋煙頭被檢控釀推撞　4食環人員受傷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170902/s00001/6fa0c7a294b0dfaaeb95675a2809be9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170902%2Fs00001%2F6fa0c7a294b0dfaaeb95675a2809be9a.jpg&h=98dbb0f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170902/s00001/6f9f91cfdc5610f33d7a45f3e82ad5c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170902%2Fs00001%2F6f9f91cfdc5610f33d7a45f3e82ad5c0.jpg&h=e5e7c708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170902/s00001/6fa1feb0b6570516f2d037c1e7f03662.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170902%2Fs00001%2F6fa1feb0b6570516f2d037c1e7f03662.jpg&h=08566683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大圍港鐵站本周五發生4名食環署人員執遇襲受傷事件，警方拘捕一名涉案男子扣查。<br />\n<br />\n遇襲受傷4名食環人員，清醒由救護車送院治理，未有大礙。被捕男子姓池，55歲，涉嫌普通襲擊罪名，報稱不適需送院檢治。<br />\n<br />\n食環署接受本報時表示，本周五傍晚約6時15分，兩名食環署小販事務隊人員在大圍火車站外執行職務期間，目擊一名男子亂拋煙蒂，遂上前採取執法行動，但該名男子拒絕出示身分證及襲擊兩名人員，人員遂要求警方協助；其間該名男子再與兩名到場增援食環署人員發生推撞。警方到場調查，4名食環署人員及涉事男子需送院治理。案件交由警方調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170902/s00001/1504285234656\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170902%2Fs00001%2F1504285234656&d=jNqal1Y62jF460GvPJUSj26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=1fc7e52e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170902%2Fs00001%2F1504285234656&h=9285109f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170902/s00001/1504285234656</a>"},{"pid":"eacb786b129639acab96c77e84cb8aa5eda13697","tid":383520,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T02:55:38.000Z","msg":"咁就放幾日假"}]}